<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>22</hymn_number>
<title>BAWIPA NA THLUACHUAH HE KAN THLAH CH22</title>
<key>Eb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa na thluachuah he kan thlah, Kan lunglawmh daihnak khahter, Na
 dawtnak cu kan co cio i, Na velngeihnak in kan tei, Thazang kan pe
 thazang kan pe, Ram car chung kan kal lioah.

[V2]
 Lawmhnak le upat kan in pek, Na Thawngtha bia lawmhnak ca'h, Na kan
 khamhnak theipar tha cu, Kan lung chungah tam ko seh, Zumhawk tlakmi kan
 siter tuah, Biatak chungah kan hmunhter.

[V3]
 Vawlei cung hin na dawtnak nih, Kannih a kan auh tikah, Thih tihnak
 kha kan teipiak tuah, Na aw thawng kha kan ngaih lai, A zungzal in a
 zungzal in, Nang he kan um ti cang lai.</lyrics>
</song>